### Welcome to PRASAD TRAINING GitHub Page.
At "prasadtraining.com" we provide User Interface Development and Testing workshops and training programs that enhance understanding, knowledge and execution of UI development on an individual as well as corporate level. Our courses and workshops cover the essentials of UI development and testing for modern websites on all standard browsers and devices. The breadth and depth of all our programs ensures holistic and practical learning.

### Authors and Contributors
Over two decades of experience in web development and training "PRASAD ALURU" has established a formal training platform for individuals and corporations

### Support or Contact
Please visit our website prasadtraining.com for more details.
